        "title": "feat(i18n): translate cron page UI strings to Simplified Chinese",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Problem: Cron page had hardcoded English strings when using Simplified Chinese locale, including job list chips (session target, wake mode, delivery mode), schedule labels, form fields (session key, account ID, light context, failure alerts), and relative timestamps.\n- Why it matters: Non-English users see English labels, descriptions, and time hints in the cron job list, creation form, and advanced options.\n- What changed:\n  - Extracted all hardcoded strings from `ui/src/ui/views/cron.ts` into i18n keys, added translations to both `en.ts` and `zh-CN.ts`.\n  - Fixed `ui/src/ui/views/cron.ts` job list chips to use localized labels for session target, wake mode, and delivery mode instead of raw values.\n  - Localized `formatCronSchedule` in `ui/src/ui/presenter.ts` using i18n keys for \"At\" and \"Every\" schedule prefixes.\n  - Added `locale` support to `formatRelativeTimestamp` in `src/infra/format-time/format-relative.ts` so UI relative times (e.g. \"8 小时后\", \"8 小时前\") are localized.\n  - Updated `ui/src/ui/format.ts` to pass the current UI locale into relative timestamp formatting.\n  - Ran `pnpm ui:i18n:sync` to propagate new keys to all locale files.\n- What did NOT change (scope boundary): No functional behavior, logic, or styling changed. No new features added. Backend cron definitions remain in English. CLI/TUI relative time formatting untouched.\n\n## Change Type (select all)\n\n- [ ] Bug fix\n- [ ] Feature\n- [ ] Refactor required for the fix\n- [ ] Docs\n- [ ] Security hardening\n- [x] Chore/infra\n\n## Scope (select all touched areas)\n\n- [ ] Gateway / orchestration\n- [ ] Skills / tool execution\n- [ ] Auth / tokens\n- [ ] Memory / storage\n- [ ] Integrations\n- [ ] API / contracts\n- [x] UI / DX\n- [ ] CI/CD / infra\n\n## Linked Issue/PR\n\n- Closes #\n- Related #\n- [ ] This PR fixes a bug or regression\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- Behavior or issue addressed: Cron page job list, creation form, advanced options, and relative timestamps were not localized to Simplified Chinese.\n- Real environment tested: Local dev gateway (`pnpm gateway:dev`).\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: Built UI assets with `pnpm ui:build`, started gateway, opened Control UI Cron tab, switched to Simplified Chinese.\n- Evidence after fix: Screenshot showing localized cron page — job list chips display \"隔离会话\", \"立即\", \"无（仅内部）\"; schedule labels show \"于 2026/5/14 03:00:00\" / \"每隔 1d\"; relative timestamps show \"13 小时后\", \"11 小时前\"; form fields show \"会话密钥\", \"账户 ID\", \"轻量上下文\", \"失败告警\", \"冷却时间（秒）\", \"告警模式\".\n\n<img width=\"2916\" height=\"1560\" alt=\"after\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9aea2bbd-96d2-412a-9cf5-2dfaaf7859f5\"/>\n\n- Observed result after fix: zh-CN locale shows fully translated cron page UI including job list, form fields, schedule labels, and relative timestamps.\n- What was not tested: Other non-English locales.\n\n## Root Cause (if applicable)\n\nN/A — not a bug fix.\n\n## Regression Test Plan (if applicable)\n\nN/A — not a bug fix or regression.\n\n## User-visible / Behavior Changes\n\n- Cron page UI now fully localized to Simplified Chinese (zh-CN).\n- Relative timestamps in Control UI now display in Chinese.\n- English locale unchanged (new keys added, existing behavior preserved).\n\n## Diagram (if applicable)\n\nN/A\n\n## Security Impact (required)\n\n- New permissions/capabilities? (`No`)\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? (`No`)\n- New/changed network calls? (`No`)\n- Command/tool execution surface changed? (`No`)\n- Data access scope changed? (`No`)\n- If any `Yes`, explain risk + mitigation:\n\n## Repro + Verification\n\n### Environment\n\n- OS: macOS\n- Runtime/container: Node 22 (local dev)\n- Model/provider: N/A\n- Integration/channel (if any): N/A\n- Relevant config (redacted): N/A\n\n### Steps\n\n1. `pnpm ui:build` to build Control UI assets\n2. `pnpm gateway:dev` to start local gateway\n3. Open Control UI in browser, navigate to Cron tab\n4. Switch locale to zh-CN (if not already)\n5. Verify job list chips, form fields, schedule labels, and relative timestamps display in Chinese\n\n### Expected\n\n- Job list chips display in Chinese: 已启用, 隔离会话, 立即\n- Schedule labels display in Chinese: 于, 每隔\n- Relative timestamps display in Chinese: 小时后, 小时前\n- Form fields display in Chinese: 会话密钥, 账户 ID, 轻量上下文, 失败告警\n\n### Actual\n\n- All above verified locally.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- [ ] Failing test/log before + passing after\n- [ ] Trace/log snippets\n- [x] Screenshot/recording\n- [ ] Perf numbers (if relevant)\n\n## Human Verification (required)\n\n- Verified scenarios: Cron tab job list, creation form, schedule labels, relative timestamps, and advanced options in zh-CN locale.\n- Edge cases checked: English locale still renders correctly (new keys added to en.ts).\n- What you did **not** verify: Other non-English locales.\n\n## Review Conversations\n\n- [x] I replied to or resolved every bot review conversation I addressed in this PR.\n- [x] I left unresolved only the conversations that still need reviewer or maintainer judgment.\n\n## Compatibility / Migration\n\n- Backward compatible? (`Yes`)\n- Config/env changes? (`No`)\n- Migration needed? (`No`)\n- If yes, exact upgrade steps:\n\n## Risks and Mitigations\n\nNone.\n",
